| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5930 — Recovery Inhibition (flocker)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e8ad2e40-0f5e-5e77-928c-cf4a66c76b1c"
